lead_paragraph: Captain Sergio Ramos believes Real Madrid are as hungry to beat Atletico Madrid in Saturday's Champions League final as they were two years ago when they beat their neighbours to land a 10th European Cup.

headline.print_headline: 2014 Victory Has Not Sated Real's Thirst for Glory-Ramos
headline.main: 2014 Victory Has Not Sated Real's Thirst for Glory-Ramos
